dc_title_s: Election Precincts: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2014
dc_description_s: This coverage represents the Board of Elections approved boundaries of the Prince George's County election precincts. While this coverage is maintained by the Prince George's County GIS Section, the boundaries are defined and their representation approved by the Board of Elections. This layer was last updated May 23, 2013.
